Ungakwazi ukumisa izilawuli zomzali ngemva kokwenza i-Google Account yengane yakho (uma ingakabi nayo), ongakwenza usebenzisa i-app ye-Google Family Link.

Sibonise izikhangiso ezenziwe zaba ngokwakho, kuya ngamasethingi wakho

Okuqukethwe okugekona okwenziwe kwaba ngokwakho kuthonywa izinto ezifana nokuqukethwe okubukayo okwamanje, umsebenzi Kuseshini yakho yokusesha esebenzayo, nendawo yakho. Izikhangiso ezingezona ezingokwakho zithonywa okuqukethwe okubukayo okwamanje nendawo yakho evamile. Okuqukethwe okwenziwe kwaba ngokwakho kanye nezikhangiso nakho kufaka phakathi imiphumela ehambisana nakakhulu, izincomo, nezikhangiso ezenzelwe wena ngokususelwe emsebenzini wasesikhathini esedlule kusuka kule divayisi, njengosesho lwe-Google lwangaphambilini. Siphinde futhi sisebenzise amakhukhi, idatha, nama-ID ukuze senze ukuzizwela kwakho kufanele abaneminyaka ethile, uma kuhambisana.

Sisebenzisa amakhukhi idatha, nama-ID ukuze silethe futhi sinakekele amasevisi we-Google, silandelele ukuphela futhi sivikele ngokumelene nogaxekile, ukukhwabanisa, nokuhlukumeza, silinganisela ukubandakanyeka kwezithameli kanye nezibalo zesayithi ukuze siqonde ukuthi amasevisi ethu asetshenziswa kanjani futhi sithuthukise ikhwalithi yalawo masevisi, sisungule futhi sithuthukise amasevisi amasha, futhi silethe futhi silinganisele ukusebenza kahle kwezikhangiso. Futhi sisebenzisa amakhukhi, idatha, nama-ID ukusekela amasethingi okwenza ngokomuntu ngamunye akuvumela ukuthi ukhethe indlela yokusebenzisa i-app ye-Google, ngisho noma uphume ngemvume.

Yenza i-Google ikubonise izikhangiso ezenzelwe wena ku-Search ezisekelwe kumsebenzi wangaphambilini ngenkathi usebenzisa le app, njengezinto oziseshayo.

Ungashintsha amasethingi akho noma kunini ngokuvula i-app yakho ye-Google futhi ufune kokuthi Amasethingi. Ungaphinda ubuyekezeInqubomgomo yethu Yobumfihlo ukuze ufunde kabanzi mayelana nokuthi i-Google ilusebenzisa kanjani ulwazi olukhiqizwa njengoba usebenzisa amasevisi we-Google.

Ukuqinisekisa amasethingi wakho kuzovumela i-Google ukuthi isebenzise amakhukhi, idatha nama-ID ukuze ikubonise okuqukethwe okwenziwe kwaba ngokwakho kanye/noma izikhangiso ezenziwe zaba ngokwakho, kuye ngezinqumo zakho.
